<h1>About App</h1>

<p>
App is the companion project to the book, <a href="http://easylaravelbook.com">Easy Laravel 5</a>, written by the bestselling author W. Jason Gilmore.
</p>

<p>
App is built atop Laravel 5 with the intent of giving fellow coders the opportunity to have a first-hand look at the many new features found in this major Laravel release. Additionally, App demonstrates numerous Laravel features of interest to beginners, including:
</p>

<ul>
<li>Blade templating</li>
<li>Model relations</li>
<li>Database queries</li>
<li>Forms integration</li>
<li>User authentication</li>
</ul>

<p>
App is released under the MIT license. You can download App on GitHub. Found a bug or a better way to do something? File an issue or submit a pull request!
</p>

<h2>Credits</h2>

<p>
The cool navbar background is Simple Dashed (created by <a href="http://venam.1.ai/">Venam</a>), and hosted on <a href="http://subtlepatterns.com/simple-dashed/">Subtle Patterns</a>. Licensed via <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/us/">CC BY-SA 3.0</a>.
</p>

<p>
Sweet tropical picture taken by little old me, copyright owner W. Jason Gilmore. I think it was taken during trip to Hawaii but it may be Puerto Rico.
</p>

